{
  "text": "We did not include samples from non-pregnant rats treated with LPS on the array, since previous research showed no physiological differences due to low-dose LPS infusion in non-pregnant animals [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . Instead, RT qPCR was used to measure gene expression in NPr + LPS rats (n = 5). We used the same 11 genes as for the validation of the array.",
  "correct_citation": {
